{"tid":1690350,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（真心膠問）米豬連認證係咪要申請先有貼紙？因為唔想自己貼完比人小","createTime":"2019-11-03T09:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T17:17:49.000Z","uid":297159,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a51e352eb29e71f3cb1881d2e7e2fb1b840ad894","tid":1690350,"uid":297159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:31:57.000Z","msg":"求教求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋間cafe 本身已經喺各大黃藍app 上咗名，但係未有連豬貼紙，想自己貼但係驚貼完比人小<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位大大可以幫下手解答下嘛？平時做開 CD-ROM ，有咩摟屌跡象出現，希望大家多多包含<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 錫個春袋都細力小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b20a528289234535cf69da470f2ae345788df79","tid":1690350,"uid":39021,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:34:18.000Z","msg":"貼完邊知係自己貼定其他人貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然幾個平台都有認證咁就貼囉<br />\n不過如果無認證都照貼就可能招惹裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a44ced60e32286bc69ce91ff2a535aa854c0f0","tid":1690350,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:34:47.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n（求人手置頂）【Twitter戰線】加入共識Channel + 有方法避免Twitter當bot同封帳！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690328\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690328</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d55baa13fdeacafb40b09d1b3d265c7192ab017e","tid":1690350,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T09:39:08.000Z","msg":"認證咗你就自己貼啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw你間cafe叫咩名 得閒嚟懲罰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69718a6b03f8eb9d33d14230d57ff3eb07dd5243","ti